author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Proact IT Group Q4 ‍EBITDA Falls To SEK 60.3 Million
text:
Feb 8 (Reuters) - PROACT IT GROUP AB:
* Q4 ‍REVENUES INCREASED BY 3% TO SEK 895 (868) MILLION​ * Q4 ‍EBITDA DECREASED BY 8% AND AMOUNTED TO SEK 60.3 (65.7) MILLION.​
* ‍PROPOSES THAT ANNUAL GENERAL MEETING SHOULD ELECT TO PAY A 2017 DIVIDEND OF SEK 3.75 (3.50) PER SHARE.​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
